videos.description: Auburn's Tyler Harris comes up with the defensive rebound and takes it all the way downt the court for the left-handed layup
videos.headline: Tyler Harris goes coast to coast for left-handed layup

videos.description: 1H (10:15) AUB Kareem Canty made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Kareem Canty dribbles between his legs before putting up big three point jumper.

videos.description: Auburn's Bryce Brown steals off of a Colorado pass and takes it all the way for a layup.
videos.headline: Bryce Brown easily steals and takes it to the hoop for a layup

videos.description: Auburn's Tyler Harris grabs his own offensive rebound and puts it back for two... seconds later Auburn steals on an inbound and Harris gets it in for two more
videos.headline: Tyler Harris scores twice in ten seconds

videos.description: Auburn's Kareem Canty crosses up Colorado's Dominique Collier, who falls to the floor, and then Canty  knocks down a wide open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Canty's ballhandling brings defender to the floor
